f="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%E1%BA%A1n-L%C3%BD/S%C6%A1-h%E1%BA%A1-thu%E1%BB%B5-kh%E1%BB%9Fi/poem-c_BKQeeUDMWE4CnkeJT9RA">Sơ hạ thuỵ khởi - 初夏睡起</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%E1%BA%A1n-L%C3%BD/author-JSRpfYAHfq-c4bVKwnYGVg">Dương Vạn Lý</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c/T%E1%BA%A1-t%C3%A2n-%C3%A2n-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-A-cg5LOiDU8UnqCmBeVIBA">Tạ tân ân kỳ 2 - 謝新恩其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c/author-x2jHtUhu4KZY4kl0A-lAIw">Lý Dục</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%A9-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/Vi%C3%AAn-Vi%C3%AAn-kh%C3%BAc/poem-33CduH4NfT9ibV757snSEw">Viên Viên khúc - 圓圓曲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%A9-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/author-clxY5GFWegDsEw0Y8VPiNQ">Ngô Vĩ Nghiệp</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-Li%C3%AAm/Vi%E1%BB%87t-ca/poem-WEJuJvnN-wODOEYeXse6lg">Việt ca - 越歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-Li%C3%AAm/author-cJEa_nnPF2Dm3ze1rqMDcA">Tống Liêm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%BF-Trinh/Vi%E1%BB%87t-Th%C3%A0nh-kh%C3%BAc/poem-FaPplw3HI2LQXVzxzE_WzA">Việt Thành khúc - 越城曲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%BF-Trinh/author-K5yGjv4-gkyzXKfuttJFiQ">Vương Thế Trinh</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
